      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Independent peer review of simulation setup and boundary condition application documented.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup independently reviewed by a second analyst. Boundary conditions, material assignments, and contact definitions verified against the simulation plan. No discrepancies identified."
