      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Model physics (linear elastic, small deformation) justified relative to observed experimental behavior and QoI.",
      "rationale": "Linear elastic material model with isotropic titanium alloy properties (Ti-6Al-4V) justified for sub-yield loading regime. Geometric nonlinearity enabled to capture rod bending. Model form appropriate for stiffness and yield load QoIs."
    },
    {
