      "acceptanceCriteria": "Material properties and geometric parameters sourced from traceable measurements or certified material specifications.",
      "rationale": "Elastic modulus and yield strength sourced from ASTM F136 certificate of conformance for each lot. Screw and rod geometry digitized from CMM measurements of test articles. Input uncertainty quantified via sensitivity analysis."
    },
