      "acceptanceCriteria": "N≥10 experimental specimens with documented traceability to production lots and dimensional inspection records.",
      "rationale": "N=11 non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs tested across two independent laboratories. All specimens from same production lot; dimensional inspection records archived. Sample size sufficient for statistical comparison."
