      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities address the same device geometry, material, and loading mode as the intended simulation use.",
      "rationale": "Validation performed on production-representative non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs under ASTM F1717 compression-bending, matching the intended FEA application. Validation domain overlap with intended use is high."
