    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for model risk level 3. The single below-threshold factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged as a credibility gap; however, the overall evidence body is judged sufficient to support the intended use of the FEA model for ASTM F1717 compression-bending performance prediction of non-cannulated pedicle screw constructs. The assessment team accepts the package with the documented gap noted for future multi-condition validation work.",
